      <ab type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">Full length shot of 6 people: a woman in dark urban clothes and a hat, and a man in military uniform with a hat with a cockade in his right hand are seated on chairs; a child is standing next to the man and leaned on his knee. Behind them are standing a young man in guarder uniform, a young woman in an urban dress with a hat, and a man in urban clothes.</ab>
      <ab subtype="comment" type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">The family of General Kliment Eftimov Boyadzhiev (1861 - 1933): wife Konstantina, the sons Alexander and Nikola, daughter Maria and grandson Kliment (son of Alexander).</ab>
